{"tid":2056173,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【街頭策略｜集思廣益】A：「你唔出係咪當手足condom？」B：「吓，你出係咪想送頭？？」","createTime":"2020-06-08T13:13:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T03:56:09.000Z","uid":176460,"like":65,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"1728666c360daa277044833d1529ff4db7fbb1ed","tid":2056173,"uid":176460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:13:26.000Z","msg":"我：「不如大家一齊思考下」<br />\n <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">今次想講街頭抗爭既樽頸</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.tenor.com/images/06e50ec37f150bd31ef0644025673a1a/tenor.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.tenor.com%2Fimages%2F06e50ec37f150bd31ef0644025673a1a%2Ftenor.gif&h=745334c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n街頭抗爭既樽頸我地已經講左好一段日子，<br />\n好多時一講呢個話題就會變左兩派手足各有各講，<br />\n一D話要繼續衝，一D話唔好送頭，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">最後都冇共識</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家都好熱衷於下一步應該點做，但係好少回顧過去我地到底做緊咩，<br />\n而我覺得呢種回顧對於定立下一步行動係好有幫助<br />\n<br />\n所以今次想係到拋磚引玉，同大家講下街頭抗爭既一個策略 &ndash;<br />\n <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">暴力邊緣論</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n係過去既一年，我諗好多人都聽過呢個Term，我都係到簡單介紹下：<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>唔知大家讀書果時有冇試過遇到D好摟打既同學，到佢真係俾人打果時佢就會搵老師報串，而最後老師就會罰打佢果個人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n暴力邊緣論大致上就係咁既一回事<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不斷挑戰對方底線，直到對方忍唔住手使用過渡既暴力，然後以此達到自己既目的</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n但係點解我地要用咁既策略呢？<br />\n首先我地睇返街頭抗爭到底有咩出路，大致上會有幾條路：<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><strong>(1) </strong>升級到武裝革命，用武力令政權屈服<br />\n<strong>(2)</strong> 出黎表達民意，然後政權接納意見並作出改善<br />\n<strong>(3)</strong> 道德感召更多人出黎反抗暴政，全民反抗，令政權無法正常運作而屈服<br />\n<strong>(4)</strong> 出黎表達民意，向世界出發尋求外力支援，等有能者打救</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n(1) 我唔會話冇可能，不過應該唔會咁快發生到<br />\n(2) 200萬人出黎證明呢條路係香港唔WORK<br />\n<br />\n<strong>剩低既就係(3)同(4)，而我地一路以黎採用既策略其實都係為左達到呢兩個目的。</strong><br />\n<br />\n打又唔夠佢打，佢平時又暗地裡恰我，同老師講佢又話冇證冇據幫我唔到。咁唯有整D證據，引佢係成班同學面前打我，到時成班同學都見到佢有幾惡，老師都冇得當睇唔到，你仲唔死？<br />\n<br />\n呢個策略係歷史上都唔少例子，香港係過去一年都證明左佢確實係有效既策略，咁繼續用呢招咪得囉，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">點解我地會遇到樽頸呢？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>主要有三個問題，而且係環環相扣：</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>(1) 畫面新鮮感流失</strong></span></span><br />\n好多畫面都係一次生兩次熟，香港第一次放TG就全世界嘩然覺得接受唔到，第二次就全世界慨嘆香港正苦死性不改。然後第三次、第四次、第一百次全世界就習慣左香港已經冇得救，都唔係D咩新鮮事。<br />\n<br />\n用作本地既道德感召可能都仲夠用，但係向世界出發既力量就會越黎越少。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔新鮮，姐係唔JUICY。唔JUICY，媒體就唔會報導。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我地可以試下反過黎用第三者角度去睇。上年係我地打得火紅火綠既時候，伊朗人民都開始左佢地既戰鬥，佢地情況比我地更惡劣，軍方好快就開實彈殺人。佢地第一兩次殺人，香港好多媒體都有報導。但係之後再殺，就越黎越少香港媒體報導，香港人對伊朗局勢既關注都隨之下降，最終伊朗死左最少200人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">(2) 政權一方既進步</span></strong></span><br />\n無意吹奏對手，但不得不承認係我地進步既同時佢地都會進步。佢地都好清楚每次佢地忍唔住手犯錯，就會製造左好多子彈俾我地做文宣。所以佢地犯錯既次數越黎越少，特別係鄧小強上任之後。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">上年11月之後，狗方使用既武力已經好少再明目張膽咁提升，莫講話實彈，2020年連TG都冇乜點放。</span></strong>取而代之既就係每日都有上門綁架，每次遊行集會都提早幾個鐘做早期介入，用限聚令罰錢取代暴力拘捕。就算開槍都係胡椒球行先，TG行後，因為難影到「靚」既畫面。<br />\n<br />\n當然唔完全係佢地既功勞，但係的確佢地都進步緊，雖然間唔中都有狗失控，但對畫面既控制無可否認係比起上年嚴密左。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">(3) 我方實力疲弱</span></strong></span><br />\n都唔需要多講，9000幾個手足被捕就係被捕，當中好多都係街頭抗爭既主力。好多案件進入司法階段，就算係本身保釋緊都仲出既手足都好難再出。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">街頭戰力每況越下</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n加上中共多次高壓干預，法院判決又不如人意，而且局勢已經升溫到大國政治層面，有部分手足會覺得已經唔到我地插手，又有好多手足心理創傷都越黎越嚴重，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">莫講話再出去打仗，留唔留係香港都成問題。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而吊詭既係「暴力邊緣論」本身就係某意義下既「苦肉計」。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果要對方持續地犯錯，我地既實力就要不斷提升去挑戰佢新既底線，但係呢條苦肉計又會令我地既實力不斷減少。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">當實力減少到已經冇辦法再觸碰對方既底線</span></strong>，街頭抗爭係咪仲要採取呢個策略，正正就係而家既樽頸。<br />\n<br />\n我知道好多手足而家都好迷惘，我自己都一樣。<br />\n但係希望大家都可以繼續思考，光復香港既路仲有好長好長。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">衝破樽頸，就靠大家一齊努力。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果呢篇文令你對下一步有多左想法，不妨留言同其他手足一齊討論下，順手推POST。</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d27cc8892e2a0cf8bd3cc785ca53973bb3179d8","tid":2056173,"uid":176460,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:13:44.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">歡迎訂閱 Telegram Channel<strong>「戰術研究學會頻道」</strong>：</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://t.me/tactics_society\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftactics_society&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19o%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=a910789b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tactics_society</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2J4dCJ3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2J4dCJ3.png&h=27184237&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>本頻道會發佈各種抗爭戰術戰略資訊，希望促進思考，一齊進步</strong></span><br />\n <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">精選重溫：</span></strong><br />\n<strong>【戰後檢討】「包圍網？夠多人就唔驚啦！」「咁早話撤，你係咪散水撚？」<br />\n</strong><a href=\"https://lih.kg/2033158\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2033158</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【戰略 + 戰術】527 527，人人都講527，你估人人都知527係做乜鳩咩？</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/axsMesU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/axsMesU</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【心態檢討】「屌曬佢地老母！如果今日係 Endgame，你去維園裸跑！」</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fxqvBS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fxqvBS</a><br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"c330c5b6a29b0ea4a860ca96de91a2391fba45e3","tid":2056173,"uid":176460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:14:45.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"855e129b881077cfc07af4c1b7db60448512c111","tid":2056173,"uid":176460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:15:37.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"2d7c1770fbd389715ebf41ec6442c1679c460dc9","tid":2056173,"uid":26876,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:16:09.000Z","msg":"Diminishing marginal returns"},{"pid":"23fb488203e1c5cfa885c43b6cd49e6857df1445","tid":2056173,"uid":176460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d7c1770fbd389715ebf41ec6442c1679c460dc9","tid":2056173,"uid":26876,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:16:09.000Z","msg":"Diminishing marginal returns"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:19:13.000Z","msg":"正是"},{"pid":"c8ecd6a1e903dbd77619879c874125c96da3e85a","tid":2056173,"uid":176460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:20:47.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"80e269e7f5c55842a990a0c018638b3616a4c401","tid":2056173,"uid":25375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:21:28.000Z","msg":"支持樓主"},{"pid":"45070c6bdb4738933e688550c7d22db868757314","tid":2056173,"uid":176460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80e269e7f5c55842a990a0c018638b3616a4c401","tid":2056173,"uid":25375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:21:28.000Z","msg":"支持樓主"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:23:11.000Z","msg":"歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb929ca7a25b06965f205abd23bc073987f0a13a","tid":2056173,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4965c7b741a864dfcc0297922a9ff8c02eade946","tid":2056173,"uid":311611,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:27:55.000Z","msg":"我只可以講政治係骯髒 只有不擇手段既人先會贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea2ec2a67fecdefcb9e67125a68943d3e6474c5","tid":2056173,"uid":25375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"45070c6bdb4738933e688550c7d22db868757314","tid":2056173,"uid":176460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80e269e7f5c55842a990a0c018638b3616a4c401","tid":2056173,"uid":25375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:21:28.000Z","msg":"支持樓主"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:23:11.000Z","msg":"歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:28:18.000Z","msg":"依家國際關注度俾BLM運動蓋過，你講嘅第(4)點效益仲低過之前<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至於(3)，除非有比之前更嚴重嘅流血事件，否則都好難道德感召更多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時我就好灰，諗唔到出路，唔知大家點睇"},{"pid":"839dacbc9353e88c37761bdc5a35e625a09cabd3","tid":2056173,"uid":139294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:29:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6b7e3573738e31bbf86c49151d1965fd7348121","tid":2056173,"uid":208308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:29:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"58c1681adb868febe357ba1c590043b9191d82d7","tid":2056173,"uid":197157,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:30:16.000Z","msg":"我真係唔明點先算係唔送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且根本唔係我地送頭，係對面濫捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db119e75fe0e963cf3e42a839978ee76d89838b6","tid":2056173,"uid":173844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:30:23.000Z","msg":"出得就預咗最低消費被捕 大圍捕<br />\n適當時候聚 唔對路就散 彈出彈入<br />\n抗爭咁耐要識走位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c16f3d091ace916fe1421500abd1f61b38d08fd","tid":2056173,"uid":1098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:34:14.000Z","msg":"就算全部行動都係送頭，都要諗點送頭先最有價值<br />\n<br />\n但無人估到結果會係點"},{"pid":"bb13b4b76920315a07987cb558df5800011615cd","tid":2056173,"uid":25375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:35:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"820bcae6c66296e13e2508e01ebe7f133a48bf09","tid":2056173,"uid":164730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:38:22.000Z","msg":"支持樓主，<br />\n<br />\n香港抗爭需要更多策論<br />\n而唔係情感舒發"},{"pid":"e3f81039272cdf427e6f3ee2208a2f914423e415","tid":2056173,"uid":23672,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:38:47.000Z","msg":"做左兩日街坊 送左兩日頭又送唔出 想同大家講下感想<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fxhrqS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fxhrqS</a>"},{"pid":"7015e51d4ea678ffb16a3cb59e6155d2709a68e5","tid":2056173,"uid":25375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:40:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c2e5d01b927fdaf65643523d822728f9b96e07dd","tid":2056173,"uid":81732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:40:55.000Z","msg":"G持！大家都要思考一下"},{"pid":"53d17666cc53dbb3ed24d0c30ba4b6fa6dc7d9e9","tid":2056173,"uid":332021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:51:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e039b44933be1d7c14fea4ea16651e3fee3702b","tid":2056173,"uid":59973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:59:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"68be7b9e592b52f69fdf55286c69997bb40d646b","tid":2056173,"uid":1098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T14:10:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b51e1161b2e8698a3bf5531471323868a3c04626","tid":2056173,"uid":333312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T16:01:35.000Z","msg":"我都一直諗緊呢個問題<br />\n但永遠都係無答案"},{"pid":"a32c0e21234e91b9e72a57386289a2787b34b8fe","tid":2056173,"uid":25375,"like":0,"disli