足做野果時可以幫下手<br />\n講到尾都只係唔甘心，但原因好多時都係活動冇明確目標"},{"pid":"e9e31648936208f186889a332253c9a28b9f87dc","tid":2056173,"uid":176460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61186deec0665484033b329eaadff6ece41f47b1","tid":2056173,"uid":282534,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T23:40:31.000Z","msg":"我反而想睇下有關 光譜改變既野 <br />\n<br />\n例如 因咩條件或者事 觸發而令光譜產生改變<br />\n<br />\n可以既話 希望文章唔只包括黃營"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T17:42:40.000Z","msg":"遲D可能會寫，但想等黃圈內部調和到先，而家仲係好唔成熟"},{"pid":"a7385d52c42497fb1520c032136e794bf9918cd6","tid":2056173,"uid":176460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2792630836110caf1ca7997863911f1dc5b2eab0","tid":2056173,"uid":37722,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T23:49:34.000Z","msg":"所以我認為現時嘅策略唔係撼動政權，而係加強/深化同路人嘅意志，簡單黎講鬥長命<br />\n<br />\n呢個唔係送頭論，唔係叫人唔好出，反而係叫人出，不過係做文宣，做宣傳戰<br />\n<br />\n要加強同路人意志，一靠行動keep住溫度（和理非遊行又好，隨街播歌播文宣整連儂牆又好），二靠思想武裝，睇多d史文哲理，搵返抗爭嘅原因，將原本情緒抗爭內化返做思想同意識形態抗爭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T17:45:24.000Z","msg":"唔係二分既，係突破樽頸之前我都同意強化左自己先，不過到突破左樽頸之後都可以兩樣一齊做。係我既立場強化自己係無論幾時都要做，唔係遇到樽頸先至做"}],"pinned":{"pid":"2d27cc8892e2a0cf8bd3cc785ca53973bb3179d8","tid":2056173,"uid":176460,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:13:44.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">歡迎訂閱 Telegram Channel<strong>「戰術研究學會頻道」</strong>：</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://t.me/tactics_society\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftactics_society&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19o%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=a910789b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tactics_society</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2J4dCJ3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2J4dCJ3.png&h=27184237&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>本頻道會發佈各種抗爭戰術戰略資訊，希望促進思考，一齊進步</strong></span><br />\n <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">精選重溫：</span></strong><br />\n<strong>【戰後檢討】「包圍網？夠多人就唔驚啦！」「咁早話撤，你係咪散水撚？」<br />\n</strong><a href=\"https://lih.kg/2033158\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2033158</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【戰略 + 戰術】527 527，人人都講527，你估人人都知527係做乜鳩咩？</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/axsMesU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/axsMesU</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【心態檢討】「屌曬佢地老母！如果今日係 Endgame，你去維園裸跑！」</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fxqvBS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fxqvBS</a><br />\n</div>"}}